      <title>民主党公布提名规则，哈里斯势头强劲 举行虚拟投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/democrats-unveil-nomination-rules-virtual-vote-as-harris-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党提议在提名过程中采用虚拟投票，并设定最低代表门槛以进行投票——这概述了竞选规则，随着副总统卡马拉·哈里斯（Kamala Harris）的退出，这场竞选可能很快就会变得毫无意义。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/democrats-unveil-nomination-rules-virtual-vote-as-harris-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 23:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
